author: Robert Kuznia and Drew Griffin, CNN
title: How did coronavirus break out? Theories abound as researchers race to solve genetic detective story
description: A vacuum of knowledge about the origins of the new coronavirus ravaging the world has provided fertile ground for all manner of theories -- from the fantastic, to the dubious to the believable.
